  "title": "Optician",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform eye refraction for customers and take necessary measurements using tools and equipment</li>\n  <li>Recommend appropriate optical aids based on findings and demands</li>\n  <li>Troubleshoot and adjust the fitting of spectacles and ophthalmic lenses</li>\n  <li>Keep and maintain customers' eye health record and historical data of purchases</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum an Advanced Certificate of Performance in Ophthalmic Dispensing and Refraction or Nitec in Opticianry</li>\n  <li>Must be eligible for registration or registered with OOB</li>\n  <li>Retail experience will be advantageous</li>\n</ul>",
